**Investigating line endings**

I’m considering if converting to CRLF will make the warning disappear and allow me to check the diff numstat accurately. First, I need to figure out the original line endings, which might be CRLF. Our Get-Content output showed `\r\n`, but after the patch, maybe it changes to LF? I should check the file bytes and use PowerShell to detect the line endings. That should help clarify the situation!
